<h3 class="wp-block-heading">ドーピング（３）＋アルティメット・ボンバリアンスペシャル</h3>



<p>観客も我々も盛り上がりは最高潮！<br>時間切れしても満足のエンターテイメントでした。</p>



<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">いろんな意味で面白かった！</h3>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="644" height="270" src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234031_380-1-644x270.png" alt="" class="wp-image-1017" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234031_380-1-644x270.png 644w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234031_380-1-300x126.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234031_380-1-768x321.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234031_380-1-1536x643.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234031_380-1-2048x857.png 2048w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234031_380-1-700x293.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px" /></figure></div>


<figure class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="644" height="270" data-id="1019" src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243-644x270.png" alt="" class="wp-image-1019" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243-644x270.png 644w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243-300x126.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243-768x321.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243-1536x643.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243-2048x857.png 2048w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234131_243-700x293.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px" /></a></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="644" height="270" data-id="1018" src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698-644x270.png" alt="" class="wp-image-1018" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698-644x270.png 644w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698-300x126.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698-768x321.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698-1536x643.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698-2048x857.png 2048w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ffxiv_20240818_234118_698-700x293.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px" /></a></figure>
</figure>



<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">クリア後の情報解禁してから</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">アタッチ・フューズボム（ぐるぐる）は野良のやり方がめちゃ簡単</h3>



<p>ぬけまる式らしいです（<a href="https://youtu.be/zZDu5NY7DIo?t=1121" data-type="link" data-id="https://youtu.be/zZDu5NY7DIo?t=1121" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">該当箇所動画</a>）</p>



<p>ぐるぐるブレスだけ避けたらあとは自分のマーカー付近で予兆を避けるだけ。</p>



<p>隣と当たらずに済むって動かなくていいし位置も悩まなくていいのでこれはめちゃ簡単。採用しました。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
